data.description: *Back on the Market, no fault to sellers or inspections* This home sits on .31 of an acre with convenient full backyard access, nestled in a culdesac, located just a few minutes from John Kilpatrick Turnpike and HWY 152 in Johnson Farms! This home offers 4 bed, PLUS a study, 2 large living areas with lots of natural lighting, 2.5 bathrooms, 3 car garage, and your very own sprinkler system. Backyard privacy as you overlook the tree scenery from back patio. The seller has recently updated paint throughout home, added granite countertops,installed a in ground storm shelter in garage and NEW ROOF is in the process. Schedule your showing today!
